title: The Outs "Novadema" - Converse Rubber Tracks: Track Of The Week
description:
The single "Novadema" by The Outs is this week's "Track of the Week". Upon arriving at Rubber Tracks Studio in Rio de Janeiro, the band got right to work testing equipment and taking advantage of the studio's extensive collection of guitar pedals. Surrounded by the nature and wildlife outside, The Outs were inspired by the studio's unique location. Inside the live room, The band laid down tracks for their first recording experience at a professional studio.

For more on Converse Rubber Tracks visit: www.converse.com/rubbertracks
